title: The Damaged
description: No longer an outsider, Bailey has a family and love that she never could’ve imagined. Used to living in the shadows, Kash will now do anything to protect his family and his woman. They will take on the world together…In the meantime, stunning motives, lies, and explosive secrets continue to unfold. 1. Quinn is in jail, awaiting trial.2. Friends might actually be enemies.3. And what is Calhoun plotting? More importantly, will Kash discover it before it’s too late?Everything will come to a head as passion and danger ignite in The Damaged.
author: Tijan
